Calls train on a model and creates a new model version given model info

Name Type Description

Properties
Name Type Description
id string Model id
name string Model name
version string Model version
type string This can be "concept", "color", "embed", "facedetect", "cluster" or "blur"
sync boolean If true, this returns after model has completely trained. If false, this immediately returns default api response.
